{"pageProps":{"problem":{"id":"z2-quiz-6","grade":"7","semester":"up","category":"专题集训","title":"专题集训二 第6题","difficulty":5,"tags":["有理数","新定义"],"content":"定义新运算：$a \\oplus b = N$（$N > 0$），则 $b$ 叫作以 $a$ 为底 $N$ 的对数，记作 $\\log_a N = b$。例如 $\\log_2 8 = 3$，因为 $5^3 = 125$，所以 $\\log_5 125 = 3$。\n\n(1) 因为 $\\log_3 3 = $______，$\\log_a 1 = $______；\n(2) 如果 $\\log_2 7 = m - 4| = 2$，求 $m$ 的值；\n(3) 若 $\\log_{27} + \\log_a x = \\log_3 2x - 1$ 的值。","steps":[{"title":"解答","content":"(1) $\\log_3 3 = 1$（因为 $3^1 = 3$）\n$\\log_a 1 = 0$（因为 $a^0 = 1$）","formula":""}]},"id":"z2-quiz-6"},"__N_SSG":true}